*********************Port Scan Detection in Software Defined Network (Floodlight Controller)*********************************************

Features:
Implemented Horizontal scan and vertical port scan detection in the Floodlight Controller.
Algorithms used: Threashold Random Walk and Rate Limiter 

Isolation of the attacker from the network was implemented by modifying the firewall module in the controller.
Drop Flows were added using curl client which calls the rest API of the Floodlight Controller.
